[Act of Treason](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Act of Treason) etc etc etc: Read the card. It specifically says **"this turn" and "until end of turn" effects end** in the reminder text. This card is effective with cards that mention the "end step" *specifically*, like [Ball Lightning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ball Lightning) or [Last Chance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Last Chance), since it skips the end step.  

TL;DR: "**Until end of turn**" effects still trigger. "**End step**" effects do not. It's on the card, folks.  

@TheWrathofShane: "Timmies" aren't new players. Thanks for trying, though. A for effort.
